cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with the problem of automatic photo adjustment, which involves image processing and computer vision techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely category as well. The paper also involves formulating the problem in a suitable way for deep learning, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with image semantics and local adjustments, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
